      {
        "signature": "void updateEgtmAtom3phInvDuty(float32 *requestDuty)",
        "behavior_description": "Synchronous immediate duty update for the three logical PWM channels. Copy requestDuty[0..2] in percent directly into the module state’s dutyCycles[0..2] (no scaling or normalization), then call the unified driver’s multi‑channel immediate update API once to apply all three duties atomically.",
        "driver_calls": [
