      {
        "signature": "void updateEgtmAtomDuty(void)",
        "behavior_description": "Incrementally adjust the three stored duty cycle values and apply them synchronously. For each logical channel i in 0..2: add the configured step (e.g., 0.01) to dutyCycles[i]; if dutyCycles[i] exceeds 100.0, wrap it to 0.0; if it is negative, clamp to 0.0. After updating all three elements, call the multi‑channel immediate PWM update API once, passing the dutyCycles array in percent to apply the changes atomically.",
